.. |codecov| image:: https://img.shields.io/codecov/c/github/wemap/django-rest-search.svg
    :target: https://codecov.io/gh/wemap/django-rest-search

.. |pypi-v| image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/djangorestsearch.svg
